text: Ðis sint ða landgemara to scroppen þorpe & þuresby.

Of langanforda dic andlang dices<../images/tbar.gif>on þa miclan dic andlang dices on blidan et celfa seyeade andlang blidan on beo lese suðewearde<../images/tbar.gif>up ða miclan strat andlang strat ut þurh beolease norð ut þone feld<../images/tbar.gif>adun on blidan up be blidan on iddil.
Up be iddel on þone fulan broc andlang broces eft on langan ford.

Ðis sint ða landgemara to suttune of fulan forda andlang stret to þam grafe þon geriht mid þone graf on þone broc andlang broces on langan ford on gerihte of scir wuda midde weardne on iddel at brodan fleote.
Ðonne is sisotef land binnan þissum gemara.
